name: CD - "Fade Away Gradually, my Hope.."
description:
MISERE NOBIS is a new rising Depressive Black Metal star from Rome, Italy. Undoubtedly, they are inspired a lot by Nyktalgia(DE).  Complex variable structure, fantastic melody and anguished wailing makes a desperate soundtrack for suicide!

Tracklist:
01. Imploro Meam Finem
02. Mors Omnia Solvit 
03. Sopor Aeternus
04. Mea Mors
05. Regnat Silentium
